We are writing a custom text editor extension using the LSP example as the baseline. We are set up to activate on YAML files:

```
"activationEvents": [
    "onLanguage:yaml"
  ],
```

In `connection.onInitialize`, we've set up the capability:

```
  result.capabilities.documentSymbolProvider = {
    label: 'Solution'
  };
```

And we have implemented `onDocumentSymbol`:

```
connection.onDocumentSymbol((params): DocumentSymbol[] => {
  logger.info('onDocumentSymbol called');
  const document = documents.get(params.textDocument.uri);
  return getDocumentSymbols(document);
});
```

I can see from the LSP server tracing that it is receiving a document symbol but the outline says that no symbols were found.

<img width="1220" alt="image" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/179807/180486733-939ea5b2-4848-41a6-a8dc-695854291b99.png">

We do get diagnostics and completions as expected, just not the outline. Are we missing something to get the outline to show?

