The issue I am running into is that, if I trigger formatter on some python file under say `python1` package, it still seems to trigger formatting via the formatter that was set for the root of the workspace. I have provided the exact client option that is being passed to create the language client. I believe i am not setting the pattern right, let me know how it should look like to work for the scenario below.

Repro configuration:
consider `multiroot.code-workspace` file with following structure. There are 3 virtual envs at different levels in the structure.
```
{
    "folders": [
        {
            "path": "notpython" // not a python project folder
        },
        {
            "path": "python1" // the python project folder that contains .venv1
        },
        {
            "path": "python2" // the python project folder that contains .venv2
        },
        {
            "path": "." // the root of the workspace also contains python files and has .venv
        }
    ],
}
```

Each of the folders gets its own LSP based formatter, this is the client config for each folder:
LS Client options used for 'notpython' workspace:
```
{
    "documentSelector": [
        { "scheme": "file", "language": "python", "pattern": "c:\\GIT\\linters\\multiroot\\multipython\\notpython/**" },
        {
            "scheme": "untitled",
            "language": "python",
            "pattern": "c:\\GIT\\linters\\multiroot\\multipython\\notpython/**"
        },
        {
            "scheme": "vscode-notebook",
            "language": "python",
            "pattern": "c:\\GIT\\linters\\multiroot\\multipython\\notpython/**"
        },
        {
            "scheme": "vscode-notebook-cell",
            "language": "python",
            "pattern": "c:\\GIT\\linters\\multiroot\\multipython\\notpython/**"
        }
    ],
    "outputChannel": { "name": "Black Formatter" },
    "traceOutputChannel": { "name": "Black Formatter" },
    "revealOutputChannelOn": 4,
    "initializationOptions": {
        "settings": {
            "workspace": "file:///c%3A/GIT/linters/multiroot/multipython/notpython",
            "trace": "error",
            "args": [],
            "path": [],
            "interpreter": ["c:\\GIT\\linters\\multiroot\\multipython\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe"]
        }
    },
    "workspaceFolder": {
        "uri": {
            "$mid": 1,
            "fsPath": "c:\\GIT\\linters\\multiroot\\multipython\\notpython",
            "_sep": 1,
            "external": "file:///c%3A/GIT/linters/multiroot/multipython/notpython",
            "path": "/c:/GIT/linters/multiroot/multipython/notpython",
            "scheme": "file"
        },
        "name": "notpython",
        "index": 0
    }
}
