            "text": "#pragma once\n\n// asdfkjghatjhkjghakasdlfkjaslrakjglaksdjtlawkjglaskdjgasdgaljtlkaewjglakjgawlekasdlgkjasdglkj asdfkjghatjhkjghakasdlfkjaslrakjglaksdjtlawkjglaskdjgasdgaljtlkaewjglakjgawlekasdlgkjasdglkj asdfkjghatjhkjghakasdlfkjaslrakjglaksdjtlawkjglaskdjgasdgaljtlkaewjglakjgawlekasdlgkjasdglkj\nnamespace trunk::bar {}  // namespace trunk::bar\n"
        }
    ]
}


[Trace - 11:39:28 AM] Sending notification 'textDocument/didOpen'.
Params: {
    "textDocument": {
        "uri": "file:///home/lauri/work/trunk/trunk/cli/actions/foo.hh",
        "languageId": "cpp",
        "version": 83,
        "text": "#pragma once\n\n// abcdef abcdef abcdef\nnamespace trunk::bar {}  // namespace trunk::bar\n"
    }
}


[Trace - 11:39:29 AM] Received response 'textDocument/formatting - (207)' in 1132ms.
Result: [
    {
        "newText": "#pragma once\n\n// abcdef abcdef abcdef\nnamespace trunk::bar {}  // namespace trunk::bar",
        "range": {
            "end": {
                "character": 4611686018427388000,
                "line": 4611686018427388000
            },
            "start": {
                "character": 0,
                "line": 0
            }
        }
    }
]


[Trace - 11:39:29 AM] Received notification 'textDocument/publishDiagnostics'.
Params: {
    "diagnostics": [],
    "uri": "file:///home/lauri/work/trunk/trunk/cli/actions/foo.hh"
}


[Trace - 11:39:29 AM] Sending notification 'textDocument/didClose'.
Params: {
    "textDocument": {
        "uri": "file:///home/lauri/work/trunk/trunk/cli/actions/foo.hh"
    }
}


[Trace - 11:39:29 AM] Sending notification 'textDocument/didChange'.
Params: {
    "textDocument": {
        "uri": "file:///home/lauri/work/trunk/trunk/cli/actions/foo.hh",
        "version": 86
    },
    "contentChanges": [
        {
            "text": "#pragma once\n\n// abcdef abcdef abcdef\nnamespace trunk::bar {}  // namespace trunk::bar\n"
        }
    ]
}


[Trace - 11:39:29 AM] Sending notification 'textDocument/didSave'.
Params: {
    "textDocument": {
        "uri": "file:///home/lauri/work/trunk/trunk/cli/actions/foo.hh"
    }
}
```

As the formatting requests occurs prior to the didChange (which is also before didOpen), it formats the old text of the file and thus the search-and-replace fails.

Presumably, the correct order should be didOpen - didChange - formatting. This may be related to https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-languageserver-node/issues/1105, although I am not sure if the fix there handles the out of order formatting request.

Let me know if you need any more info. Much appreciated!

